---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="How AI Governance Affects Company Valuation | FTSE 250 & AIM Guide | AiLex Consulting"
  description="Systematic analysis of AI governance impact on public company valuations. ESG enhancement, risk mitigation, and investor confidence for FTSE 250 and AIM companies."
>
  <Header />
  
  <main>
    <!-- Professional Hero -->
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-blue-50 py-16">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <div class="inline-block bg-white rounded-lg px-6 py-2 mb-6 shadow-sm">
            <span style="font-family: Georgia, serif; color: #1a365d; font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.875rem; letter-spacing: 0.05em;">
              SCIENTIA ET LEX
            </span>
          </div>
          <h1 style="font-family: Georgia, serif; font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: bold; color: #1a365d; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
            AI Governance Impact on Company Valuation
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
            Systematic analysis of AI governance influence on public company valuations. Risk mitigation quantification, ESG enhancement assessment, and investor confidence evaluation for FTSE 250 and AIM companies.
          </p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mt-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 shadow-sm">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold" style="color: #22543d;">+23.8%</div>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Valuation premium</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 shadow-sm">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold" style="color: #dc2626;">€35M</div>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Penalty mitigation</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 shadow-sm">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold" style="color: #2d3748;">87%</div>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Investor preference</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 shadow-sm">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold" style="color: #1a365d;">15%</div>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">ESG score enhancement</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Systematic Valuation Impact Framework -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 style="font-family: Georgia, serif; font-size: 2rem; font-weight: bold; color: #1a365d; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
            Systematic Valuation Impact Framework
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">Quantified governance influence on shareholder value creation</p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-8">
          <!-- Risk Mitigation Value -->
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-8">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-white mr-4" style="background-color: #dc2626;">1</div>
              <h3 style="font-family: Georgia, serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; color: #dc2626;">
                Risk Mitigation & Penalty Avoidance
              </h3>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold mb-3" style="color: #2d3748;">Regulatory Protection</h4>
                <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-700">
                  <li>• EU AI Act penalty avoidance (€35M maximum)</li>
                  <li>• Risk-adjusted discount rate reduction (1.5-2.5%)</li>
                  <li>• Compliance cost optimisation</li>
                  <li>• Reputational risk mitigation</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold mb-3" style="color: #2d3748;">Financial Impact</h4>
                <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-700">
                  <li>• Protected cash flows from enforcement</li>
                  <li>• Reduced insurance premiums</li>
                  <li>• Lower legal and compliance costs</li>
                  <li>• Business continuity assurance</li>
                </ul>
                <div class="mt-4 p-3 rounded-lg" style="background-color: #fef2f2;">
                  <div class="text-lg font-bold" style="color: #dc2626;">8-12% premium</div>
                  <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">From risk mitigation alone</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- ESG Enhancement -->
          <div class="rounded-xl p-8" style="background-color: #f0fff4;">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-white mr-4" style="background-color: #22543d;">2</div>
              <h3 style="font-family: Georgia, serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; color: #22543d;">
                ESG Performance & Investor Appeal
              </h3>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold mb-3" style="color: #2d3748;">ESG Enhancement</h4>
                <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-700">
                  <li>• Responsible AI governance scores</li>
                  <li>• Stakeholder trust improvement</li>
                  <li>• Transparency and accountability</li>
                  <li>• Sustainable practice demonstration</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold mb-3" style="color: #2d3748;">Investment Benefits</h4>
                <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-700">
                  <li>• ESG fund access expansion</li>
                  <li>• Reduced cost of capital</li>
                  <li>• Enhanced institutional interest</li>
                  <li>• Improved analyst coverage</li>
                </ul>
                <div class="mt-4 p-3 rounded-lg" style="background-color: #f0fff4;">
                  <div class="text-lg font-bold" style="color: #22543d;">6-10% premium</div>
                  <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">From ESG enhancement</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Operational Excellence -->
          <div class="rounded-xl p-8" style="background-color: #f0f9ff;">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-white mr-4" style="background-color: #1a365d;">3</div>
              <h3 style="font-family: Georgia, serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; color: #1a365d;">
                Operational Excellence & Market Leadership
              </h3>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold mb-3" style="color: #2d3748;">Process Optimisation</h4>
                <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-700">
                  <li>• Systematic AI deployment procedures</li>
                  <li>• Enhanced system reliability</li>
                  <li>• Accelerated innovation cycles</li>
                  <li>• Data quality improvements</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold mb-3" style="color: #2d3748;">Competitive Positioning</h4>
                <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-700">
                  <li>• Market leadership recognition</li>
                  <li>• Customer trust enhancement</li>
                  <li>• Strategic partnership opportunities</li>
                  <li>• Talent attraction advantages</li>
                </ul>
                <div class="mt-4 p-3 rounded-lg" style="background-color: #f0f9ff;">
                  <div class="text-lg font-bold" style="color: #1a365d;">4-8% premium</div>
                  <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">From operational excellence</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Sector-Specific Analysis -->
    <section class="py-16" style="background-color: #f7fafc;">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 style="font-family: Georgia, serif; font-size: 2rem; font-weight: bold; color: #1a365d; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
            Sector-Specific Valuation Impact Analysis
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">FTSE 250 & AIM sector governance premiums</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-8">
          <!-- Financial Services -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
            <h3 style="font-family: Georgia, serif; font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: bold; color: #1a365d; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
              Financial Services
            </h3>
            <div class="text-center mb-4">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold" style="color: #1a365d;">+18.5%</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Average premium</div>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <li>• Credit scoring compliance</li>
              <li>• Algorithmic trading transparency</li>
              <li>• Regulatory capital efficiency</li>
              <li>• Customer trust enhancement</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Healthcare & Life Sciences -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
            <h3 style="font-family: Georgia, serif; font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: bold; color: #22543d; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
              Healthcare & Life Sciences
            </h3>
            <div class="text-center mb-4">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold" style="color: #22543d;">+22.3%</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Average premium</div>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <li>• Medical AI safety compliance</li>
              <li>• Patient data protection</li>
              <li>• Clinical trial optimisation</li>
              <li>• Regulatory approval acceleration</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Technology & Software -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
            <h3 style="font-family: Georgia, serif; font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: bold; color: #2d3748; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
              Technology & Software
            </h3>
            <div class="text-center mb-4">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold" style="color: #2d3748;">+25.7%</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Average premium</div>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <li>• Product liability protection</li>
              <li>• Enterprise customer confidence</li>
              <li>• Platform trust enhancement</li>
              <li>• Global market access</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Public Company Requirements -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm">
          <h3 style="font-family: Georgia, serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; color: #1a365d; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
            Public Company Governance Requirements
          </h3>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold mb-3" style="color: #2d3748;">Board & Investor Framework</h4>
              <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-700">
                <li>• Board-level AI oversight structures</li>
                <li>• Quarterly governance reporting</li>
                <li>• ESG metric integration</li>
                <li>• Investor disclosure compliance</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold mb-3" style="color: #2d3748;">Regulatory Compliance</h4>
              <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-700">
                <li>• EU AI Act documentation</li>
                <li>• Risk management integration</li>
                <li>• Transparency obligations</li>
                <li>• Audit readiness maintenance</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Professional Consultation -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <h2 style="font-family: Georgia, serif; font-size: 2rem; font-weight: bold; color: #1a365d; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
          Professional Valuation Impact Assessment
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Systematic AI governance valuation analysis necessitates specialised regulatory expertise combined with public market understanding to ensure accurate investor confidence enhancement and ESG integration.
        </p>
        
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-8 mb-8">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 text-center">
            <div>
              <div class="text-lg font-bold" style="color: #1a365d;">Board Readiness</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">£15,000 governance assessment</div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-lg font-bold" style="color: #22543d;">ESG Integration</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">£25,000 programme development</div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-lg font-bold" style="color: #2d3748;">Investor Relations</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">£10,000 strategy support</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4 md:space-y-0 md:space-x-4 md:flex md:justify-center">
          <a 
            href="/emergency-assessment" 
            class="inline-block px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold text-white transition-colors shadow-lg"
            style="background-color: #1a365d;"
            onmouseover="this.style.backgroundColor='#2c5282'"
            onmouseout="this.style.backgroundColor='#1a365d'"
          >
            Request Valuation Assessment
          </a>
          <a 
            href="/contact" 
            class="inline-block px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors border-2"
            style="border-color: #1a365d; color: #1a365d;"
            onmouseover="this.style.backgroundColor='#1a365d'; this.style.color='white'"
            onmouseout="this.style.backgroundColor='transparent'; this.style.color='#1a365d'"
          >
            Discuss Governance Strategy
          </a>
        </div>
        
        <p class="text-gray-600 mt-6">
          FTSE 250 & AIM specialisation • ESG enhancement • Board-ready frameworks
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>